{"title":"东风万里送喜讯","authors":["王恩宇"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风万里送喜讯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京第一机床厂工人　王恩宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风万里送喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯震动着我们的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在昆仑山巅大声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利了的是中国人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人，中国人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢的骨头铁的筋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两年中——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几度炼钢炉边眠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几度洪水里稳立身……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱涝中夺得大丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生来就有降龙伏虎劲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党——伟大的舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾驶着阶级的巨轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年的航程两年走完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是：中国式的大跃进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！群山举臂欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！江河放声歌吟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里东风万里歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂党的大功勋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“沉舟侧畔千帆过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病树前头万木春。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你虫儿一旁噪叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们仍要策马飞奔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风万里送喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯万里增干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢炉中火正红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那是我们的跃进心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空气锤声震天地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——那是我们的浑身劲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来年腊梅再开时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看：我们的胜利更惊人！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}